[p 
	"Once Buster Bunny and his friends were cleaning up a room in the warehouse of Acme Looniversity. They noticed a piece of paper turned out to be a very old treasure map. But Montana Max took it away from Buster and got Dr. Gene Splicer to help him search for the treasure. Buster's friends were brainwashed or kidnapped by mad scientist and he has to rescue them, then to find the treasure and stop Montana Max.
	$LF
]p
